{"id":75,"date":"2017-07-04T08:11:26","date_gmt":"2017-07-04T08:11:26","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/?p=75"},"modified":"2017-07-04T08:11:29","modified_gmt":"2017-07-04T08:11:29","slug":"nhung-kien-thuc-co-ban-ban-can-biet-truoc-khi-di-du-lich-nhat-ban","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/nhung-kien-thuc-co-ban-ban-can-biet-truoc-khi-di-du-lich-nhat-ban\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i du l\u1ecbch Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ed1n m\u00f9a thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t: m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n v\u1edbi hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o n\u1edf d\u1ea7n t\u1eeb nam l\u00ean b\u1eafc, m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u00e2y c\u1ed1i xanh m\u01b0\u1edbt, m\u00f9a thu l\u00e1 phong (momiji) \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eafm t\u1eeb b\u1eafc xu\u1ed1ng nam, m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng tuy\u1ebft tr\u1eafng tinh kh\u00f4i. Ng\u1ecdn N\u00fai Ph\u00fa S\u0129 (Fujisan) cao nh\u1ea5t <strong>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/strong>, n\u1eb1m gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 tuy\u1ebft bao ph\u1ee7 n\u01a1i ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai, l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u0103n s\u0129 v\u00e0 thi s\u0129 <strong>x\u1ee9 Ph\u00f9 Tang<\/strong> c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c v\u0103n ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia v\u00e0 h\u1ecda s\u0129 kh\u1eafp b\u1ed1n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch <strong>du l\u1ecbch Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/strong> c\u0169ng v\u1eady.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4073\" src=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/nhung-kien-thuc-co-ban-ban-can-biet-truoc-khi-di-du-lich-nhat-ban-75.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/nhung-kien-thuc-co-ban-ban-can-biet-truoc-khi-di-du-lich-nhat-ban-75.jpg 800w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-nhat-ban-1-300x201.jpg 300w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-nhat-ban-1-768x515.jpg 768w\" alt=\"du l\u1ecbch Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Tham quan v\u00e0 \u0111i l\u1ea1i<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn khi du l\u1ecbch Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: C\u1ee5m ch\u00f9a chi\u1ec1n, \u0111\u1ec1n th\u1edd \u1edf 3 trung t\u00e2m v\u0103n h\u00f3a: Tokyo, Kyoto v\u00e0 Osaka; C\u00e1c khu nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1eddn, nu\u00f4i tr\u1ed3ng bonsai; N\u00fai Ph\u00fa S\u0129 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean ng\u1eafm hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o; \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea7m hoa t\u1eed \u0111\u1eb1ng Kawachi Fuji \u1edf Fukuoka. C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean Hitachi \u1edf qu\u1eadn Ibaraki; R\u1eebng tre Sagano \u1edf ph\u00eda t\u00e2y b\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Kyoto; H\u1ebbm n\u00fai Shiratani Unsuikyo; \u0110\u1ed3i c\u00e1t Tottori \u1edf Chugoku; Trang tr\u1ea1i hoa lavender \u1edf Hokkaido; L\u00e0ng c\u1ed5 Gokayama v\u00e0 L\u00e0ng Zao Kitsune \u1edf Miyagi\u2026.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4074\" src=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/nhung-kien-thuc-co-ban-ban-can-biet-truoc-khi-di-du-lich-nhat-ban-75-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/nhung-kien-thuc-co-ban-ban-can-biet-truoc-khi-di-du-lich-nhat-ban-75-1.jpg 800w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-nhat-ban-2-300x201.jpg 300w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-nhat-ban-2-768x515.jpg 768w\" alt=\"du l\u1ecbch Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng giao th\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng c\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u00e2n ti\u1ebfn. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n g\u1ed3m t\u00e0u \u0111i\u1ec7n ng\u1ea7m cao t\u1ed1c, t\u00e0u n\u1ed5i v\u00e0 xe bus. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<p><strong>H\u00e0nh l\u00fd v\u00e0 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 4 m\u00f9a Xu\u00e2n, H\u1ea1, Thu, \u0110\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. M\u00f9a xu\u00e2n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 5, M\u00f9a H\u1ea1 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 6 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 8, M\u00f9a Thu t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 9 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 11 v\u00e0 m\u00f9a \u0110\u00f4ng t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 12 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m sau.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4075\" src=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/nhung-kien-thuc-co-ban-ban-can-biet-truoc-khi-di-du-lich-nhat-ban-75-2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/nhung-kien-thuc-co-ban-ban-can-biet-truoc-khi-di-du-lich-nhat-ban-75-2.jpg 800w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-nhat-ban-3-300x201.jpg 300w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-nhat-ban-3-768x515.jpg 768w\" alt=\"du l\u1ecbch Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u00f9a h\u1ea1 \u1edf <strong>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/strong> ch\u00eanh nhau t\u1edbi tr\u00ean 30 \u0111\u1ed9 C. V\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u1ea1, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cao l\u00e0m cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ee5c th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. C\u00f2n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n v\u00e0 m\u00f9a thu th\u00ec kh\u00ed h\u1eadu r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu nh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng thay \u0111\u1ed5i. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a thu, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e3o ph\u00e1t sinh \u1edf v\u00f9ng ph\u00eda t\u00e2y c\u1ee7a B\u1eafc Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ed9 v\u00e0o Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00f4i khi g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1\u1ecb v\u00e8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u1ee7a. V\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 v\u00f9ng n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt c\u0169ng c\u00f3 tuy\u1ebft r\u01a1i.<\/p>\n<p>Khi \u0111i sang Nh\u1eadt, du kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean mang trang ph\u1ee5c g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9, \u0111\u1ee7 \u1ea5m. N\u00ean mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1o thun. Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1o n\u1eb7ng. Mang theo kh\u0103n qu\u00e0ng c\u1ed5, n\u00f3n, gi\u00e0y th\u1ea5p \u2013 b\u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c \u0111i l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i ch\u00f9a, l\u0103ng t\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c trang ph\u1ee5c k\u00edn \u0111\u00e1o (nam: tr\u00e1nh \u00e1o thun ba l\u1ed5, qu\u1ea7n short).<\/p>\n<p>M\u00f9a \u0110\u00f4ng : Du kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean mang theo \u00e1o kho\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u00e0y, n\u00f3n, g\u0103ng tay b\u1eb1ng len ho\u1eb7c da, kh\u0103n cho\u00e0ng c\u1ed5, son m\u00f4i gi\u1eef \u1ea9m, body lotion,\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ed1n m\u00f9a thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t: m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n v\u1edbi hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o n\u1edf d\u1ea7n t\u1eeb nam l\u00ean b\u1eafc, m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u00e2y c\u1ed1i xanh m\u01b0\u1edbt, m\u00f9a thu l\u00e1 phong (momiji) \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eafm t\u1eeb b\u1eafc xu\u1ed1ng nam, m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng tuy\u1ebft tr\u1eafng tinh kh\u00f4i. [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":76,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[19],"tags":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/75"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=75"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/75\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":80,"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/75\/revisions\/80"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/76"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=75"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=75"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=75"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}